collections.name: Landscape Top 2025
collections.description:
The Forgotten Legend

Hidden within one of Voxely's lands lies an abandoned city called "Novax," once home to the brightest virtual civilization. However, its inhabitants mysteriously vanished, leaving behind only magnificent structures and cryptic temples. Some say they disappeared into the blockchain, waiting for someone to free them.

Each Voxely landscape you see is a gateway to this mysterious world. By owning a piece of this land, you not only possess a digital artwork but also a fragment of a lost history. Are you ready to unlock these secrets and become part of this endless world?

This collection of Voxely landscapes is designed for collectors seeking digital art, deep stories, and a unique experience in the metaverse. The future, shaped by each piece, is in your hands.

♯ Cyberpunk JAPAN 🏯

🌸 Neon lights meet ancient traditions 🌸

Welcome to Cyberpunk JAPAN, a collection that fuses the spirit of Japan's ancient traditions with the electrifying aesthetics of a cyberpunk future.

Traditional meets futuristic.

collections.name: Lucky - Creator's Edition
collections.description:
Lucky’s Legacy is a tribute to an unforgettable companion who embodied unconditional love, care, kindness, and loyalty. Each NFT in this collection captures his unique essence, immortalizing his story in the digital world.

Lucky is a symbol of love and devotion, inspiring us to become better every day.

This collection is more than digital art—it is a celebration of the deep emotional bonds we share with our pets. Each piece is a 1/1 edition, ensuring exclusivity and lasting value. This NFT is a personal and exclusive edition, owned permanently by its creator.

collections.name: PososCafe
collections.description:
“Después del último sorbo, lo que queda cuenta una historia. Esta pieza abstracta captura la esencia de los posos de café en el fondo de una taza: residuos del tiempo, fragmentos de pensamiento y la huella de momentos fugaces. En su caos aparente, se esconde un lenguaje secreto, un mapa de azar y destino. Esta obra es un testimonio visual de la belleza en lo efímero.”
• Formato: NFT 1/1 (Único)
• Técnica: Arte digital y animación
• Inspiración: La textura de los posos de café y su simbolismo en la interpretación del destino
• Blockchain: Ethereum/Polygon

collections.name: Neon Muses
collections.description:
Step into a world where art meets algorithms — Neon Muses is a captivating collection of AI-generated portraits that blur the line between reality and imagination. Each piece embodies ethereal beauty, vibrant color palettes and surreal detail, bringing to life characters from an alternate digital universe.

From soft pastel hues to bold neon lights, these muses represent the fusion of human creativity and machine intelligence. Every portrait in this collection is unique, highlighting distinct features, emotions and aesthetic styles crafted through advanced AI techniques.

Whether you see them as reflections of future beings or dreamlike visions from parallel worlds, each Neon Muse invites you to connect with the evolving story of art in the digital age.

collections.name: Wildlife
collections.description:
Wildlife Collection – A Tribute to Nature's Wonders

Welcome to the Wildlife Collection, a limited-edition collection of NFTs celebrating the beauty and diversity of wildlife. This collection includes digital photographs and artwork depicting unique animals such as the majestic ocelot and the charming duck. Each NFT is limited to a certain number and highlights special features or rare perspectives that reflect the lives of these animals and their habitat.

The collection features animals from different regions of the world, captured in vibrant colors and details. Part of the proceeds goes towards protecting wild animals and preserving their natural habitats.

Don't miss the chance to become part of the wildlife community. Discover the fascinating creatures of this earth and support the preservation of nature - in a strictly limited collection!

collections.name: Krugger
collections.description:
NFT Collection: The Secrets of the Krugger Family 🕯️🔪
Blood calls. The curse lingers. The story is far from over...

Step into the darkness with The Secrets of the Krugger Family, an exclusive collection of limited-edition NFTs, inspired by the sinister events that shaped the fate of this cursed lineage. From forbidden rituals to the shadows that still whisper their names, each NFT is a digital relic of terror, a fragment of a story that few dare to uncover.

👁️ What does this collection hide?
🔹 Unique and limited-edition NFTs inspired by the darkest members of the Krugger family.
🔹 Priority access to “The Secret of the Kruggers”, the most VIP and terrifying experience at Insomnia Corporation.
🔹 Exclusive lore fragments, revealing untold secrets of the Krugger curse.
🔹 Unlockable special content, offering clues for future horror experiences.

Each NFT is more than an image: it’s a key to the past, an encrypted curse on the blockchain.

The Krugger family never rests...
